result.name: Cheung Sing Restaurant

reviews.text: No frills local tea restaurant. Can't go wrong with their pork chops
A good choice for quick bite and most importantly not pricy. A lot of variety and always offer something not on the menu. Very good and friendly servers. Tasty and not expensive.  Recommended.

Very good Hong Kong style breakfast. The price is okay, we are two persons usually eating for 64 hkd.
I only tried it for breakfast. The food is not making you full super long, but it taste good as well as their Hong Kong styled milk tea.
Good food, value for money! Must try👍
Typical hk style cafe.

reviews.text: 吉列猪排😶一😶正
麻甩佬飯堂，蔥油雞扒飯，好食。
豬扒好味，牛扒，牛舌及炸雞肶、雞翼都很好，碟頭飯好好味。
No frills local tea restaurant. Can't go wrong with their pork chops
當然要吃我最喜愛的蕃茄炸雞髀意粉或者蕃茄牛脷燴意粉，記得要加太陽蛋哦！
